methods.getSubView:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

Obtain a Full-Subscription View of this StreamGenerator that can be sent to a single subscriber.

*Overload 1*  
  :param options: (io.deephaven.grpc_api_client.barrage.chunk.ChunkInputStreamGenerator.Options) - serialization options for this specific view
  :param isInitialSnapshot: (boolean) - indicates whether or not this is the first snapshot for the listener
  :param viewport: (io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.Index) - is the position-space viewport
  :param keyspaceViewport: (io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.Index) - is the key-space viewport
  :param subscribedColumns: (java.util.BitSet) - are the columns subscribed for this view
  :return: (io.deephaven.grpc_api.barrage.BarrageStreamGenerator.SubView) a MessageView filtered by the subscription properties that can be sent to that subscriber
